TextEng: Who's this Dergiab you mention?
And you look more like a prisoner, to me.
I could kill you, you know.
Text: 내가 널 죽일 수도 있어, 알아둬.

TextEng: You don't seem happy to see your rescuer.
Then leave for the surface, and quickly.
I'll not give you the chance to backstab me!
Text: 네가 날 배신할 기회는 안 줄 거야!

TextEng: Answer my questions, and I'll consider your fate.
Text: 내 질문에 답해, 그럼 네 운명을 고려해 보지.

TextEng: So you're some kind of prisoner, then?
I don't need your help. Go on.
You had your chance! Prepare to die!
If you can help me, then do so before I kill you.
Text: 날 도울 수 있다면, 죽이기 전에 어서 말해.

TextEng: Why would I want to fight him?
Dergiab was your partner?
Tell me more about this cult he fell in with.
Text: 그가 빠진 사교에 대해 더 말해줘.

TextEng: I don't need to hear any more. You're free to go.
Text: 더 들을 필요 없어. 가도 좋아.

TextEng: That's enough. Time to die!
What were you recruiting an army for and how big has it gotten?
Text: 군대를 모은 목적이 뭐고, 얼마나 커졌어?

TextEng: Tell me more about this cultist.
Text: 그 사교 신도에 대해 더 말해줘.

TextEng: Do you know what purpose the cult wanted the army for?
You is prisoner? Ha!
What is Dergiab? Person?
What? Me here to rescue you!
Me can kills you too easy! If me wants!
Goodbye.
Bye-bye.
Why me wants fighting Dergiab?
Me not stopping you. Go. Leave.
If you answers questions, me let you live. Maybe.
So you is prisoner here? Why that is?
Me not like prisoner. Me kill prisoner!
Text: 나 죄수 싫어. 나 죄수 죽여!

TextEng: Me not needs you help. You go.
Text: 나 너 도움 필요 없어. 너 가.

TextEng: If you gots stuff to say, saying it now!
That it! You say it! Me kill you!
Me not hear more. You go free.
Text: 나 더 안 들어. 너 자유야.

TextEng: Dergiab? Is you partner, yes?
Tells me on cult Dergiab in.
What you need army for and how big it is?
Text: 군대 뭐 하려고 만들었어? 얼마나 커?

TextEng: Me want know more of cultist.
Text: 나 사교 신도 더 알고 싶어.

TextEng: What cult want army for? You know?
Text: 사교 군대 뭐 하려고 만들어? 알아?
